title: Peter Thomas Roth Gentle Complexion Correction Pads (60 Pads)
description: Winner for "Best Peel" in Allure Magazine's 2009 Best of Beauty awards! Cleansing pads reduce the appearance of fine lines, clear up blackheads and refine pores.  Regulates healthy cell turnover and delivers proven anti-aging benefits that help reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. Deluxe, generously thick, double-sided pads deliver gentle cleansing action on one side and superior pore-refining exfoliation on the textured side. Pads contain a potent blend of Alpha Hydroxy Acid (Glycolic Acid 10%), Beta Hydroxy Acid (Salicylic Acid 0.5%) and Alcohol (23%) in an advanced botanical formulation. Fresh peach bellini scent replaces traditional medicinal antiseptic pads.
